    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/d0ec99305d6257db9fafab64872be1d5.poster.avif?t=1771309922\" width=616 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/d0ec99305d6257db9fafab64872be1d5.webm?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/d0ec99305d6257db9fafab64872be1d5.mp4?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Double Time 是一款適合任何年齡段的有趣且充滿活力的遊戲。 遊戲非常有活力； 它訓練您的反應，並包含訓練眼部肌肉的有用練習。 你知道它嗎？ 到處都是肌肉。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/cbd28936bdd859e935108007852f35c9.poster.avif?t=1771309922\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/cbd28936bdd859e935108007852f35c9.webm?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/cbd28936bdd859e935108007852f35c9.mp4?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>遊戲特點：您將獲得一定的時間。 每次用球擊中硬幣時，您將獲得 5 秒的額外時間。 擊中目標越多，打破記錄的機會就越大，收集 55 個硬幣<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/edade0160bdd5bfa1d8dc9b920f5acb4.poster.avif?t=1771309922\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/edade0160bdd5bfa1d8dc9b920f5acb4.webm?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1862010/extras/edade0160bdd5bfa1d8dc9b920f5acb4.mp4?t=1771309922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>然而，一切都沒有那麼容易。 你會有敵人，他們會試圖通過向你射擊來破壞你。 你需要抵抗他們，記住時間！",
